<view class="container">
  <view wx:if="{{!start}}">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="title">
        “
      </view>
      <view class="question">
        欢迎来到我们的性格测试环节，这里有{{ subject.length }}道题目，可以测出你的性格特征哦
      </view>
    </view>
    <view>
    <view class="answer normal">
      <view class="button" bindtap='start'>
        开始测试
      </view>
    </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{start && !finish}}">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="title">
        “
      </view>
      <view class="question">
        {{ subject[index].title }}
      </view>
      <view class="process">
        {{ index + 1 }} / {{ subject.length }}
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="answer">
      <view class="button" data-answer="a" bindtap="chooseAnswer">
        {{ subject[index].a }}
      </view>
      <view class="button" data-answer="b" bindtap="chooseAnswer">
        {{ subject[index].b }}    
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{finish}}">
    <view class="card">
      <view class="title">
        恭喜
      </view>
      <view class="question">
        你的性格测试已经完成啦，但是为了得到更准确的数据，你还需要多写几篇真情流露的日记呢，稍后可在个人页面查看性格分析
      </view>
    </view>
    <view>
    <view class="answer normal">
      <view class="button" bindtap='end'>
        完成测试
      </view>
    </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>